<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/174192-i-m-actually-working-on-my-thesis-and-i">I&#39;m actually working on my thesis, and I chose existentialism as a theme. Unlike neitzsche and many other existentialists Arab philosophers do believe in the existence of God, they adopted neoplatonism in their philosophy (that the natural wolrd is a series of emanations of the naature of God)So I kinda wanted to bring the Arab philosophy to subject, so is this book helpful?</a>
</div>
