<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Well this book actually contradicts the emanation and every other neoplatonism ; if you are looking for neoplatonism go for Ibn Sina and Al-Farabi ...<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Well this book actually contradicts the emanation and every other neoplatonism ; if you are looking for neoplatonism go for Ibn Sina and Al-Farabi ...<br />Because Al-Ghazali is based purely on the holy book and not on any other philosophy, for him they are all heretics (including greeks and every person that was inspired from them- if you need any help contact me - PS : i'm working on Neitzsche) <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
