<span id="freeTextContainer10764056494365023367">It is amazing that someone writing so long ago and in such a different culture can so accurately pinpoint what is wrong with &apos;modern&apos; thinking. It is also intriguing to get an insight into the era when Islamic culture was the flower of civilization.</span>
  <span id="freeText10764056494365023367" style="display:none">It is amazing that someone writing so long ago and in such a different culture can so accurately pinpoint what is wrong with 'modern' thinking. It is also intriguing to get an insight into the era when Islamic culture was the flower of civilization.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10764056494365023367" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

